onNdefPushComplete(android.nfc.NfcEvent).Description: Called on successful NDEF push. This callback is usually made on a binder thread (not the UI thread).
onNdefPushComplete(android.nfc.NfcEvent).history: Added in API level 14 Deprecated in API level 29

ClassDesc: this feature is deprecated. File sharing can work using other technology like Bluetooth. A callback to be invoked when the system successfully delivers your @B_android#nfc#NdefMessage_E@ to another device.
